Name: UCSB
Description: A great university located along the California coast!

Name: PV Cove
Description: A wonderful cove located off the cliffs of Palos Verdes where you will find surfers all throughout the day.

Name: Waikiki Beach
Description: A beautiful beach filled with tourists who come to see the great nature of Honolulu.

Name: Cloud Gate
Description: Also called 'The Bean" this is a very popular monument located in the midst of Chicago and created using steel plates that were welded together like a puzzle.

Name: Staples Center
Description: A world class sports and entertainment venue that hosts anything from concerts to basketball and hockey games.

Name: Waimea Bay
Description: A bay with clear waters located on the shores of Honolulu. In the summer you will find cliffjumping and snorkeling and in the winter you will find waves up to 40 ft.
